<title type="html"><![CDATA[04/06 (Thu) The Killer Whale Mom’s love/ The singer Liu’s death?  (Host: Zoe)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=715&amp;p=743#p743"><![CDATA[
We will hold an on-site meeting only.<br />摩斯漢堡明曜店(每人低消 :60元)<br />台北市仁愛路4段151巷37號地下室.<br />MRT忠孝敦化站3號出口 , 明曜百貨後方第二個巷子口<br /><br />Royal 台北 ( Thursday )<br />**** NEW***     Meeting time agenda:7:00-9:00 PM<br />7:00-7:30  Chatting time with your favorite drink, and introduction of the meeting by the host<br />7:30-8:00  discussion of the first topic<br />8:00-8:05  Take a group photo<br />8:05-8:30  discussion of the second topic<br />8:30-9:00  Individual Presentation<span style="font-weight: bold"><span style="color: #FF0000">         (we will be divided into two groups, <br />each person will have two minutes to give a presentation on any topic of that day. <br />The host will keep the time and each person will switch after two minutes. <br /> )</span></span><br /><br />--------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br /><br /><span style="font-weight: bold">Session 1.</span> Orca mothers forgo having more offspring to look after full-grown sons<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://edition.cnn.com/2023/02/09/world/killer-whale-mothers-sons-scli-intl-scn">https://edition.cnn.com/2023/02/09/worl ... i-intl-scn</a><!-- m --><br />1.What are your thoughts on this article?<br />2.Do you think parents should care for their children when they are adults? <br />3.How do you identify &quot;mama's boy or girl&quot;?<br />4.Does a mother love every child the same?<br />5.Whether the gender inequality still persist in Taiwan?<br /><br /><span style="font-weight: bold">Session 2.</span> Ex-agent says he made up news of singer Liu’s death<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.taipeitimes.com/News/taiwan/archives/2023/02/17/2003794520">https://www.taipeitimes.com/News/taiwan ... 2003794520</a><!-- m --><br /><br />1.     How much do you know about Liu Wen Zheng?<br />2.Do you think there is any difference between past superstars and current ones?<br />3.     Which classic variety show do you miss the most?<br />4.     Which celebrity do you wish could come back to life?<br />5.     How should we deal with fake news?<br /><br /><br />P.S.<br />1.參加三次(含實體及線上會議)後，只要繳交1,000元(學生500元)，即可成為ROYAL終身會員!<br />2.請帶著開放的心與熱情來參加全英文會話聚會!<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=55735">zoe</a> — Sun Apr 02, 2023 9:37 am</p><hr />
